thread.title_full: Movoto Real Estate reviewed by Donna

author: Donna
title: Donna
text: Dave found me exactly what I was looking for! And informed me about the condo before it was listed on the market. I am so pleased! My experience with him has been very pleasant. He kept me apprised of properties on a daily basis, and always answered my questions promptly. He also accommodated me for showings, and was very knowledgeable about the properties that we visited. Now that I have a deposit on my new house, he still looks out for my best interests. I would recommend him to anyone.
